title: Shanina Shaik shows off pert derriere as she arrives at Hyde in Los Angeles
text:
Shanina Shaik showed off her incredible figure on Saturday.

The 28-year-old had posed on the red carpet in a white bodysuit dress with a dramatic train while hosting the 2019 UNICEF Masquerade Ball in Los Angeles.

She then headed off to hot spot Hyde, showing off her cheeky outfit on the way there.

Flashing for fashion! Shanina Shaik stepped out in a dramatic white bodysuit as she arrived at Hyde in Los Angeles on Saturday

The model flaunted her pert derriere in the very high-cut dress and a pair of black tights.

The front of the frock featured a huge bow detailing, while remaining quite skimpy at the back.

A pair of strappy stilettos added to the effect of the high-fashion ensemble.

Wow! The model flaunted her pert derriere in the very high-cut dress and a pair of black tights

Cheeky: The front of the frock featured a huge bow detailing, while remaining quite skimpy at the back

She strode confidentially into the venue as if it were a runway, stopping to strike a pose.

Earlier, the beauty had showed off her famous figure on the red carpet at the UNICEF Masquerade Ball.

The Victoria's Secret model slicked her extra long hair extensions into a high ponytail with plait.

Model magic! She strode confidentially into the venue as if it were a runway, stopping to strike a pose

She drew attention to silver jewels on the eyelid and under eye area and lashings of mascara.

Bold brows, contoured cheekbones and a nude lipstick finished off her beauty look.

Shanina captured the event's festivities on her Instagram Stories, particularly Billie Eilish's performance.
description: Shanina Shaik showed off her incredible figure on Saturday.
authors: Marta Jary For Daily Mail Australia
